ySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"彩","body":"有點想看看是怎麼樣的派對跟Live，\n但是那天有PasPale的工作……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"ev98-ep5-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"花音","body":"不用勉強沒關係唷。聖誕節不是只有聖誕老公公，\n偶像也是很忙的。工作加油唷！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"ev98-ep5-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"彩","body":"謝謝～！但是，為了讓聖誕老公公綻開微笑，\n心心們真是想了很厲害的事情呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"ev98-ep5-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"花音","body":"是呢。聽到的時候，我也覺得很棒呢。\n能夠回禮給為了一直帶給孩子們微笑\n而努力的聖誕老公公呢","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"ev98-ep5-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"彩","body":"呵呵，能夠自然就想到那邊，\n小音不愧是「HelloHappy」的人呢！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"ev98-ep5-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"花音","body":"唔，唔嗯……因為從小時候開始，\n只要到了聖誕節就會為了聖誕老公公準備餅乾跟牛奶，\n所以就自然而然的這麼想了吧","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"ev98-ep5-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"彩","body":"餅乾和牛奶？","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"ev98-ep5-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":14}],"windowDisplayName":"花音","body":"好像在海外比較會有的風俗，\n聖誕節的夜裡準備餅乾跟牛奶放在枕邊，\n好好招待聖誕老公公","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":14,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":14,"voiceId":"ev98-ep5-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId"